editable.description: Controls whether a cell's editor is editable/readonly

breakpointMargin.description: Controls if the cell has a margin to support the breakpoint UI

hasExecutionOrder.description: Whether the execution order indicator will be displayed

executionOrder.description: The order in which this cell was executed

statusMessage.description: A status message to be shown in the cell's status bar

runStartTime.description: If the cell is running, the time at which the cell started running

lastRunDuration.description: The total duration of the cell's last run

inputCollapsed.description: Whether a code cell's editor is collapsed

outputCollapsed.description: Whether a code cell's outputs are collapsed
